        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         <BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=2 face="Verdana" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote>edit : btw, how difficult is it to get a thurg / warlocks robe from the mobs in kael? how many raids am i lookin at?<hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana" size=2 id=quote>Depends entirely on how big a bite your guild can take out of Kael.</P><P>If you can handle the arena, then abandon hope of ever seeing the robe drop.  Oh sure, it CAN happen, but the chances in the arena are only slightly better than nil.</P><P>If you can handle the Sentinels around Tormax or the Armors of Zek in the temple, then you have a much better chance of seeing the robe drop.</P><P>Overall, drop rates in Kael blow goats...if you can handle the Tormax or Temple areas, skip Kael entirely and head to HoT.</P><P></P><P>--Nergal Teir'Draconis, Children of the Phoenix (Tunare)<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
